Hey! :wave:
_A little late on the intro (whoops!)._ 

Evgeni from :flag-bg: here. Currently I work with <https://fantasticservices.com/|Fantastic Services> to help them better position themselves as an industry leader in the franchise space. At the moment I'm leading a 70+ page website project meant to be the driving force behind the company's growth, as they get in more countries. Before that, I worked on their Australian content strategy, that's was the stepping stone to what is currently read by more than 100,000 people per month.

I'm also the ink-slinger at <https://onload.agency/|Onload> and the brains behind my tiny, but mighty copywriting shop <http://briefercopy.com/|Brief-er> where I work with brands and people to help them find their true voice.

<https://www.linkedin.com/in/evgeni-asenov/|Let's connect>!

text:
Greetings! This is quite an impressive group. I’m honored to be here. <https://www.happytoil.com|Happy Toil> is an email-focused digital studio where I spend most of my time. My background is UX and product leadership, but since going independent almost 3 years ago have found a good fit in email. Beyond that my wife and I homeschool our four young kids and are getting ready to hit the road for a yearlong “family adventure” through the United States.

Looking forward to getting to know some of you.
